reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Don’t run with socks on, on this rug! 😂 You will fall. OTHER than that minor downfall, I love it! It’s soft, and holding up well with three kids under 8, two adults, a cat and a dog.Slightly hard to vacuum, it’s not heavy so the suction on my vacuum has to be turned down as low as it goes otherwise I physically cannot vacuum it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great size for a big room, great for accent to any room. Love my color, fluffiness and it unfolds nicely.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great for the price!
reviews.reviewText: We actually have this in two sizes. I love that it comes folded up in a vacuum bag so it isn’t some big bulky thing to get delivered and it is very soft and looks nice. The only thing I don’t love is that it is difficult to vacuum so if your dog eats a biscuit and drops some pieces it’s difficult to get them out sometimes. But it lays flat, doesn’t slip, and doesn’t seem to stain very easy. So overall it’s a good purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So soft and easy to clean!
reviews.reviewText: I was a little worred about cleaning one of these rugs but I've cleaned it a few times now since May with no issues! Love this rug the design is so pretty and its so soft! Its fluffy enough ur wanna dig you're feet in them! Definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Definitely not more than a throw rug
reviews.reviewText: Lesson learned, trust past purchasers reviews. Whereas it is very soft, no padding or cushion and not anymore luxurious than a Walmart throw rug. I’d ship back if it wasn’t such a pain.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Rug is very soft
reviews.reviewText: This rug looked pretty in my room however it was very thin. It definitely needs a pad under it to make it comfy to walk on. I did return it. I received it very quickly and packed in a box.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft, affordable rug
reviews.reviewText: This rug is SO soft, it's not too thick, we got it for a living room rug, but I got it too small so we put it my kids room and it's perfect for him to sit on while he's playing. Super affordable!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice and soft
reviews.reviewText: This rug was a winner. I returned it only because it was the wrong color brown for my room. I was sad.
